## Sending a Push with Payload

Payload can be defined through 2 possible parameters

1. `-p '{"postId":1}'`
1. `-f payload.json`

Examples

```
pushtester send ios -t TITLE -m MESSAGE tool -d YOUR_DEVICE_TOKEN -p '{"postId":1}'
```

